  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So before, you know, you could kind of organize yourself and establish some kind of a routine and-- and rules of behavior and-- and order, we were gone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was Shavuot, but I'm not certain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I really have no recollection of dates and-- and exact timing, although it's recorded and I-- and I've seen it, but I-- I simply don't remember it myself now.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The year was 1944, in May.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It must have been-- you know, we must have been put into the ghetto in the last days of April or the first days of May.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by May 29, we were deported.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 19.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- yeah, I was 19 the preceding March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we talked very little, to tell you the-- the truth, because we were so dang busy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What little organization, what little provision, what little, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, burying of people, what-- what little attempt to bring medication and some-- whatever kind of [INAUDIBLE] to the-- to the afflicted was-- was us, a few young people.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were supposed-- we were supposed to be-- I too was in what they called the ghetto police, which was headed by one of the prominent assimilated Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and it shouldn't be-- I shouldn't even call it that, because it had no relationship to what we know about the ghettos of Poland, or the police-- the Jewish police of the ghettos of Poland, and no relationship whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were sort of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not so much maintain order as well as carrying out the orders that were given to the Jews via the console.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
